
{{< example go >}}

```go

func main() {
	pulumi.Run(func(ctx *pulumi.Context) error {
		test, err := ltm.LookupNode(ctx, &ltm.LookupNodeArgs{

			Partition: "Common",
		}, nil)
		if err != nil {
			return err
		}
		ctx.Export("bigipNode", test.Address)
		return nil
	})
}
```
